{"title":"最大公约数和最小公倍数","uid":"bf78c7f6bd375a5822ed23ea851e116a","slug":"最大公约数和最小公倍数","date":"2021-11-13T15:18:41.000Z","updated":"2021-11-13T15:54:14.588Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/最大公约数和最小公倍数.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>2</p>\n<h1 id=\"最大公约数和最小公倍数\"><a href=\"#最大公约数和最小公倍数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"最大公约数和最小公倍数\"></a>最大公约数和最小公倍数</h1><p>输入两个正整数m和n，求其最大公约数和最小公倍数。</p>\n<p><strong>输入</strong></p>\n<p>两个整数</p>\n<p><strong>输出</strong></p>\n<p>最大公约数，最小公倍数</p>\n<p><strong>样例输入复制</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight basic\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"symbol\">5 </span><span class=\"number\">7</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>样例输出复制</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight basic\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"symbol\">1 </span><span class=\"number\">35</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>思路</strong>:</p>\n<p>首先我们需要了解，最小公因数和最小公倍数的相关性质</p>\n<p>两数的乘积 / 最大公因数 = 最小公倍数</p>\n<p><strong>所以要求最大公因数和最小公倍数，只需求出其一就可直接利用性质，完成题目。</strong></p>\n<p>辗转相除法是古希腊求两个正整数的最大公约数的，也叫欧几里德算法，其方法是用较大的数除以较小的数，上面较小的除数和得出的余数构成新的一对数，继续做上面的除法，直到出现能够整除的两个数，其中较小的数（即除数）就是最大公约数。以求288和123的最大公约数为例，操作如下：</p>\n<p>288 % 123 == 42</p>\n<p>123 % 42 == 39</p>\n<p>42 % 39 ==  3</p>\n<p>39 % 3 == 0</p>\n<p>此时3 就是288和 133的最大公约数</p>\n<p>结构大致如此 , num1 num2 使用大数取模小数</p>\n<p>t = m% n</p>\n<p>m  = n</p>\n<p>n = t</p>\n<h2 id=\"代码如下\"><a href=\"#代码如下\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码如下\"></a>代码如下</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">using namespace std;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n,m,num1,num2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">//输入两个数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> t = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcin &gt;&gt; num1 &gt;&gt; num2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tm = num1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tn = num2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(m&gt;n)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//进入循环 辗转相除</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(t != <span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tt = m % n;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tm = n;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tn = t;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//求最小公倍数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> b = (num1*num2) / m; </span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tcout &lt;&lt; m &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">&quot; &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; b &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(m &lt; n)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(t!=<span class=\"number\">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tt = n % m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tn = m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tm = t;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> b = (num1*num2)/n;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tcout &lt;&lt; n &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">&quot; &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; b;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(m==n)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//直接输出最小公倍数 公约数都相同</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tcout &lt;&lt; n &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">&quot; &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; n &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","text":"2 最大公约数和最小公倍数输入两个正整数m和n，求其最大公约数和最小公倍数。 输入 两个整数 输出 最大公约数，最小公倍数 样例输入复制 15 7 样例输出复制 11 35 思路: 首先我们需要了解，最小公因数和最小公倍数的相关性质 两数的乘积 / 最大公因数 = 最小公倍数 所...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.2k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"算法解题","slug":"算法解题","count":2,"path":"api/tags/算法解题.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"